description:
Welcome to February’s SWmobile event, kindly hosted this month by the folks at Just Eat.

Talks
- We are living in a post-agile world (Holly Bowman & Chris Rodd)
- I ❤️ Charles (Proxy) (Scott Alexander-Bown)
- Instant Apps, ytho? (David Branton)
- Chomping at the Bit(rise) (Daniel Leivers)
- App Experimentation with Optimizely X (Dave Jones)

Timings
18:30 Doors, Food & Drink
19:00 Talks
19:50 Break
20:00 More talks!
20:50 Tidy up
21:00 Head to a local pub to continue the conversation

As always we welcome new speakers. Please message the organisers if you have a talk idea, or fill out the form at http://cfp.swmobile.org
